.SH NAME
commitbrief-completion-powershell - Generate the autocompletion script for powershell


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcommitbrief completion powershell [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate the autocompletion script for powershell.

.PP
To load completions in your current shell session:

.EX
commitbrief completion powershell | Out-String | Invoke-Expression
.EE

.PP
To load completions for every new session, add the output of the above command
to your powershell profile.


